What you need to know:  The highway links the country to South Sudan, Ethiopia, and countries to the south of KenyaThe three-kilometre deadly Kamatira is steep and is adjacent to a valleyEfforts by the government to curb fatal crashes on the notorious stretch have yielded no resultsThe deadliest accident happened in 2000 when 60 soldiers died at the spot after their lorry veered off the road and plunged into a ditch